<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="#Therapeutic_uses_of_cognitive_reframing"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Therapeutic uses of cognitive reframing</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-3"><a href="#Humour_and_cognitive_reframing"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Humour and cognitive reframing</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#Differentiated_from_cognitive_restructuring_and_distortion"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Differentiated from cognitive restructuring and distortion</span></a></li>
